## Objective

The `responseBuffers` Map in `telegram/outbound.ts` has no cleanup mechanism. If an agent crashes without sending `done` or `error`, the buffer persists indefinitely, causing a memory leak. Add TTL reaping matching the Slack adapter's pattern.

